# mattermost-plugin-community-admin

Plugin ID: `com.lalbers.community-admin` — delegated organizer user management (Go server + React webapp).

Repo: https://github.com/lucas-albers-lz4/mattermost-plugin-community-admin  
Deployed via sibling **mattermost-oci-deploy** (`install-community-admin-plugin.sh`).

## Build and quality

```sh
make install-dev-tools && make setup-hooks   # once
go test ./...
make dist                                    # → dist/com.lalbers.community-admin-*.tar.gz
```

Pre-commit runs: gitleaks (staged), go vet, golangci-lint (incl. gosec), go test, govulncheck (optional).

## E2E / manual test

- `e2e/` — Playwright + `scripts/api-smoke.sh`; secrets in `e2e/.env` only (gitignored)
- Requires workstation IP in deploy repo `TEST_ALLOWED_CIDR`
- Test Mattermost started via deploy repo `manage-test-instance.sh`
- After plugin install on test: use `mmctl plugin add` (not raw copy to `/mattermost/plugins/` — wiped on restart)
- Webapp bundle path quirk: may need copy to `/mattermost/client/com.lalbers.community-admin/` — see `docs/operations.md`

## Code layout

- `server/` — API, authz, mmctl password reset (`EnableLocalMode` required)
- `webapp/src/` — RHS panel, ScopeEditor; `window.__communityAdminOpenPanel` for e2e only
- Docs: `docs/`; do not duplicate long guides in README

## Agent defaults

- Module/import path: `github.com/lalbers/mattermost-plugin-community-admin`
- Minimal diffs; do not commit `e2e/.env` or `dist/`
- Do not commit or push unless explicitly asked
